$	zip --password mypassword tecmint.zip file-name 1.txt file-name 2.sh file-name 1.js  

$	unzip tecmint.zip


7-zip

Install:
$	sudo apt-get install p7zip-full

Usage:
Compress files into zip using 7-zip and encrypt it
$	7za a -tzip -p -mem=AES256 tecmint.zip file-name 1.txt file-name 2.sh file-name 1.js
enter password

Decompress encrypted zip file using 7-zip.
$	7za e tecmint.zip










